{"tid":1677231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"啟德站暫定1月5日啟用","createTime":"2019-10-27T03:40:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T04:26:30.000Z","uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a4068a801191bedec475e4918362a002f82e007d","tid":1677231,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:40:24.000Z","msg":"沙中線紅磡站去年起接連被揭發工程醜聞，導致原定今年中通車的屯馬線大圍站至紅磡站一直押後。政府早前指，「屯馬線一期」，由大圍站至啟德站將率先在明年首季通車。<br />\n<br />\n據《香港01》取得港鐵內部文件，當中提及屯馬線第一期通車日期，暫定為明年1月5日，而下周一（28日）將會開始試車營運。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵回覆《香港01》證實，屯馬線一期於下周一起進入試營運階段，至於通車日期仍有待落實。"},{"pid":"27849ce82704e2473cd6999e77a301a13356de9b","tid":1677231,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:41:05.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"839602ac23e3a2ffad7abb81c038aef2a064800a","tid":1677231,"uid":121095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:57:57.000Z","msg":"成條沙中線都豆腐渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52a0823c09fda7366277db497c245e04f4ff764","tid":1677231,"uid":17646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:59:02.000Z","msg":"一開站就比人爆"},{"pid":"27640c2868e6742a4400324c5efe02ff7aad6289","tid":1677231,"uid":165028,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"c52a0823c09fda7366277db497c245e04f4ff764","tid":1677231,"uid":17646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:59:02.000Z","msg":"一開站就比人爆"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T04:00:08.000Z","msg":"到時都冇人搞啦"},{"pid":"9c059b53d64d0d6dc87f817caae57ba617b00bc2","tid":1677231,"uid":17646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"27640c2868e6742a4400324c5efe02ff7aad6289","tid":1677231,"uid":165028,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"c52a0823c09fda7366277db497c245e04f4ff764","tid":1677231,"uid